    {
      "text": "Mushi no Idokoro is a puzzle game about insects in a fantasy world.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "The game features 3 game modes: 1 - Ranking Mode: Compete against time 2 - Story Mode: Advance through a story mode clearing the different puzzles. 3 - Battle Mode: Play against another human player to clear the cube first. The game features also a Movie Mode in which the player can watch the movies that he unlocked in the story mode.",
